    <h1>Revenue Intelligence</h1>
    <p class="description">An AI-driven approach that automatically captures every customer interaction — emails, calls, meetings — and turns it into <strong>forecast accuracy, deal health scores, and pipeline insights</strong> your team can act on.</p>
